---
By: Ralph W. Trine
Source:
  ID: 57c5499b-c3b2-4b09-92a9-a6e977a32050
  Locus:
    Page: 309
    Verse: 18
Tags:
  - Love
---
Put love into the world and heaven with all its beauties and glories becomes
a reality. Not to love is not to live, or to live a living death. The
life that goes out in love to all is the life that is full, and rich, and
continually expanding in beauty and in power.
